2%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Distorted%20images%20of%20a%20woman's%20face%20and%20a%20silhouette%20of%20a%20woman%20texting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689cce93cfc04e97619b5ad3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20ago%2C%20Ahmet%20Tozal%20took%20out%20three%20credit%20card%20loans%20and%20withdrew%20his%20life%20savings%20to%20make%20a%20fortune%20off%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2044-year-old%20Turkish%20garment%20worker%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Istanbul%20at%20the%20time%2C%20said%20he'd%20been%20goaded%20by%20a%20new%20friend%20who%20contacted%20him%20via%20a%20random%20WhatsApp%20message%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20claimed%20she'd%20messaged%20him%20accidentally%2C%20but%20was%20friendly%20and%20seemed%20interested%20in%20Turkey%2C%20Tozal%20said.%20She%20told%20him%20she%20was%20a%20wealthy%20businesswoman%20who%20would%20soon%20be%20visiting%20his%20country%20on%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%20said%20she%20sent%20him%20dozens%20of%20photos%20of%20herself%2C%20a%20young%20East%20Asian%20woman%20traveling%20the%20world%20and%20attending%20prestigious%20conferences.%20He%20said%20they%20video-called%20once%2C%20for%20a%20few%20seconds.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20suggested%20he%20try%20investing%20in%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trajectory%20of%20their%20relationship%20has%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20what%20global%20authorities%20call%20a%20classic%20pig-butchering%20scam%2C%20typically%20run%20by%20gangs%20in%20Asia.%20Tozal%20said%20that%20over%20several%20weeks%2C%20the%20woman%20convinced%20him%20to%20invest%20about%20400%2C000%20Turkish%20lira%2C%20or%20a%20year's%20worth%20of%20his%20wages%2C%20into%20a%20cryptocurrency%20called%20UAI%20Coin.%20It%20never%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%20told%20me%20he%20lost%20everything.%20Saddled%20with%20debt%20and%20broke%2C%20Tozal%20moved%20alone%20to%20Uzbekistan%20to%20find%20a%20higher%20salary%20that%20could%20feed%20his%20family%20and%20pay%20off%20an%20extra%20200%2C000%20lira%20in%20loan%20interest.%20His%20wife%20and%20four%20children%20stayed%20behind%20in%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20think%20about%20it%2C%20it%20makes%20one%20almost%20go%20mad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20on%20a%20call%20from%20his%20shared%20apartment%20in%20Andijan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPig-butchering%2C%20a%20crypto%20scam%20that%20started%20in%20China%2C%20is%20now%20a%20global%20crisis.%20It%20draws%20its%20name%20from%20the%20concept%20of%20fattening%20a%20pig%20before%20slaughter%3A%20The%20purveyors%20build%20a%20relationship%20with%20a%20mark%20over%20weeks%20or%20months%20before%20persuading%20them%20to%20give%20away%20or%20invest%20large%20sums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202024%20University%20of%20Texas%20study%20estimated%20that%20%2475%20billion%20has%20been%20lost%20to%20such%20schemes%20since%202020.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20Heartland%20Tri-State%20Bank%20in%20Kansas%20went%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F08%2F21%2Fcryptocurrency-shan-hanes-pig-butchering-scam.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebankrupt%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20its%20CEO%20poured%20%2447%20million%20of%20company%20cash%20into%20a%20similar%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%20has%20little%20chance%20of%20recovering%20his%20money%2C%20and%20dozens%20of%20other%20men%20say%20they%20were%20fooled%20by%20the%20same%20scam.%20Betrayed%20and%20desperate%20for%20any%20restitution%20possible%2C%20they%20latched%20onto%20the%20only%20lead%20they%20could%20find%3A%20the%20woman%20behind%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWho%20was%20she%3F%20Each%20of%20the%20men%20had%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20her%2C%20the%20young%20East%20Asian%20woman%20who%20seemed%20to%20be%20living%20the%20high%20life%2C%20but%20not%20much%20else%20to%20go%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20hunted%20for%20answers%2C%20their%20stories%20of%20loss%20and%20grievance%20would%20come%20to%20haunt%20a%20person%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away%2C%20a%20millennial%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20name%20for%20herself%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20as%20he%20was%20lured%20into%20the%20crypto%20trap%2C%20Tozal%20knew%20her%20only%20as%20Dora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20nine%20months%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20men%20from%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20many%20in%20Central%20and%20West%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20who%20say%20they've%20been%20affected%20by%20this%20specific%20pig-butchering%20scam.%20While%20their%20experiences%20varied%2C%20each%20one%20was%20tricked%20with%20the%20likeness%20of%20the%20same%20Asian%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeven%20of%20these%20men%2C%20including%20Tozal%2C%20agreed%20to%20full%20interviews.%20I%20verified%20all%20of%20their%20identities%2C%20and%20they%20showed%20me%20evidence%20of%20their%20online%20interactions.%20Several%20also%20showed%20me%20screenshots%20of%20their%20financial%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20were%20unwilling%20to%20be%20named%20and%20said%20they%20did%20not%20report%20their%20losses%20to%20the%20authorities%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20seen%20as%20fools%20and%20damaging%20their%20reputations.%20Some%20said%20they'd%20fallen%20in%20love%20with%20their%20WhatsApp%20acquaintance%3B%20Tozal%20said%20he%20and%20Dora%20were%20strictly%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshots%20show%20conversations%20with%20scam%20workers%20posing%20as%20women%20like%20%26quot%3BDora.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689d8ddf194a2d49b8ae8bcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20men%20received%20cold%20texts%20from%20a%20woman%20claiming%20to%20have%20extensive%20experience%20in%20investments.%3Cp%3EScreenshots%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20come%20from%20different%20companies%20and%20walks%20of%20life.%20The%20common%20denominator%3F%20They%20all%20had%20jobs%20and%20thus%20a%20source%20of%20cash.%20Aamy%20Ace%2C%20a%2044-year-old%20Indian%20pharmaceutical%20manufacturing%20worker%2C%20said%20he%20was%20cheated%20out%20of%20%2412%2C000%20meant%20for%20his%20father's%20cancer%20treatment.%20Another%20man%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20Kazakhstani%20restaurant%20manager%20in%20Almaty%20named%20Amir%2C%20said%20he%20borrowed%20and%20lost%20%248%2C000%20%E2%80%94%2010%20times%20his%20monthly%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20remember%20different%20names.%20Some%20said%20they%20spoke%20to%20%26quot%3BJasmine%26quot%3B%20for%20weeks%2C%20while%20others%20knew%20her%20as%20%26quot%3BAnna.%26quot%3B%20Several%2C%20like%20Tozal%2C%20told%20me%20their%20contact%20was%20%26quot%3BDora.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20playbook%20for%20this%20scam%20is%20standardized.%20Men%20like%20Tozal%20would%20receive%20a%20cold%20text%20and%20slowly%20be%20persuaded%20to%20strike%20up%20a%20friendship%20or%20romance%20with%20the%20texter.%20All%20were%20sent%20photos%20of%20the%20same%20young%20Asian%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20very%20standard%20hook%20is%20an%20attractive%20person%2C%20male%20or%20female%2C%20coming%20in%20and%20saying%3A%20'Oh%20yeah%2C%20I%20have%20a%20business%20opportunity%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20come%20see%20you%20soon%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Joshua%20James%2C%20a%20cybercrime%20coordinator%20in%20Bangkok%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Office%20on%20Drugs%20and%20Crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20their%20contacts%20convinced%20them%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20fake%20asset.%20Most%20of%20the%20men%20said%20they%20put%20their%20money%20into%20a%20faux%20cryptocurrency%20called%20UAI%20Coin.%20A%20mobile%20app%20and%20fake%20trading%20website%20lent%20a%20sheen%20of%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20profits%20seemed%20eye-watering.%20Erdi%20Bilgi%C3%A7%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20Turkish%20electrician%20in%20Zonguldak%2C%20told%20me%20his%20initial%20%24100%20investment%20turned%20into%20%24500%20overnight%20in%20late%202023.%20Bilgi%C3%A7%2C%20calling%20himself%20an%20avid%20investor%2C%20said%20he%20tracks%20stock%20prices%20and%20bitcoin%20almost%20daily%2C%20and%20felt%20UAI%20Coin's%20prices%20moved%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20when%20he%20withdrew%20his%20initial%20gains%2C%20he%20received%20the%20full%20sum%20in%20his%20bank%20account.%20Emboldened%2C%20he%20took%20out%20a%20%241%2C500%20loan%20at%20Dora's%20behest%2C%20gathered%20his%20life's%20savings%20of%20about%20%2410%2C000%2C%20and%20put%20them%20all%20in%20UAI%20Coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20told%20me%3A%20'Sell%20your%20car%2C%20sell%20this%2C%20sell%20that%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f9f3ba5-eef5-44be-a7ee-f28f62b231d2%5C%22%3ELosing%20it%20all%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20Tozal%20and%20Bilgi%C3%A7%2C%20it%20seemed%20as%20though%20there%20was%20only%20one%20woman%20contacting%20them.%20But%20scam%20gangs%2C%20many%20based%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20are%20known%20to%20force%20human-trafficked%20victims%20to%20work%20in%20teams%2C%20sometimes%20with%20multiple%20people%20posing%20as%20the%20same%20woman%20in%20conversation%20with%20a%20mark.%20The%20US%20Institute%20of%20Peace%20estimated%20in%202024%20that%20some%20220%2C000%20trafficked%20victims%20are%20involved%20in%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudging%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20testimonies%20of%20survivors%20of%20human%20trafficking%20coming%20from%20scam%20compounds%2C%20many%20of%20them%20were%20being%20asked%20to%20pose%20as%20attractive%20young%20ladies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mina%20Chiang%2C%20founder%20of%20Humanity%20Research%20Consultancy%2C%20a%20UK-registered%20anti-trafficking%20social%20enterprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20their%20ploy%20more%20convincing%2C%20gangs%20have%20a%20woman%20take%20part%20in%20occasional%20video%20calls%20or%20voice%20messages.%20Several%20men%20in%20the%20Dora%20scam%20told%20me%20they%20received%20voice%20messages%20and%20forwarded%20them%20to%20me.%20A%20few%2C%20including%20Tozal%2C%20also%20said%20they%20had%20brief%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tactics%20helped%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20Dora%20was%20real%2C%20they%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20men's%20savings%20are%20invested%2C%20the%20critical%20point%20of%20the%20scam%20unfolds.%20The%20victims%20discover%20they%20can't%20withdraw%20their%20funds%2C%20and%20the%20scammers%20try%20squeezing%20them%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%20said%20he%20asked%20Dora%20for%20help%20and%20was%20directed%20to%20pay%20a%20tax-related%20fine%20to%20unlock%20his%20account.%20When%20that%20didn't%20work%2C%20he%20said%2C%20an%20engineer's%20fee%20was%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20knew%20then%20that%20he'd%20been%20fooled.%20The%20funds%20he%20lost%2C%20including%20his%20debt%2C%20are%20worth%20about%20%2415%2C000%20now%2C%20in%20a%20country%20where%20the%20average%20worker%20earns%20%247%2C300%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20what%20it%20is.%20My%20money%20is%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20Tozal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20said%20they've%20lost%20even%20more.%20A%2050-year-old%20Turkish%20academic%20in%20Ankara%20said%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20sold%20their%20apartment%20to%20save%20for%20a%20new%20city-center%20flat%20and%20dumped%20that%20money%2C%20along%20with%20%2450%2C000%20he%20convinced%20relatives%20to%20invest%2C%20into%20UAI%20Coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20showed%20me%20a%20police%20report%20he%20made%20in%20Ankara%2C%20in%20which%20he%20reported%20losing%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000%20to%20the%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20myself%2C%20how%20am%20I%20going%20to%20live%3F%20I%20can%20survive%2C%20but%20I%20have%20a%20daughter%20in%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Now%2C%20he%20added%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20are%20working%20weekends%20and%20second%20jobs%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d693b9da-166c-4015-885a-044216e12efb%5C%22%3EFinding%20Dora%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20spring%20of%202024%2C%20the%20group%20scamming%20Tozal%20appeared%20to%20make%20a%20mistake.%20As%20the%20men%20nursed%20their%20wounded%20pride%2C%20some%20received%20an%20email%20offering%20further%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221386%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20an%20email%20sent%20by%20scammers%20perpetuating%20the%20UAI%20Coin%20scam.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689d8adfcfc04e97619b64c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sample%20email%20from%20the%20gang%20running%20the%20UAI%20Coin%20scam.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sender%20neglected%20to%20blind%20carbon%20copy%20each%20victim's%20email%20address%2C%20and%20the%20men%20began%20to%20contact%20each%20other.%20They%20gathered%20on%20WhatsApp%20groups%20and%20social%20media%2C%20swapping%20stories%20of%20how%20they'd%20been%20fooled%20by%20UAI%20Coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20they%20realized%20they'd%20all%20been%20talking%20to%20the%20same%20woman.%20Younger%20ones%2C%20like%20Bilgi%C3%A7%20the%20electrician%2C%20put%20her%20photos%20into%20a%20reverse%20Google%20image%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20someone.%20She%20wasn't%20Dora%2C%20or%20Jasmine%2C%20or%20Anna%3A%20Her%20name%20was%20Abe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20be%20sure%20100%25%20it's%20her%2C%20but%20the%20videos%20and%20photos%20that%20we%20saw%20online%20were%20consistent%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilgi%C3%A7%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbe%20is%20a%20Malaysian%20woman%2C%20they%20learned.%20She%20lives%20over%205%2C000%20miles%20from%20Tozal%20and%20Bilgi%C3%A7%20and%20runs%20a%20public%20Instagram%20account.%20Her%20name%20quickly%20spread%20among%20the%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20those%20like%20Tozal%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20the%20first%20real%20step%20to%20getting%20their%20money%20back.%20But%20as%20I%20soon%20discovered%2C%20this%20woman%20wasn't%20the%20mastermind%20of%20an%20audacious%20lonelyhearts%20scam%3B%20she%20was%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAbe%20Lim%20was%2020%20minutes%20late%20when%20we%20met%20at%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur's%20upscale%20shopping%20district.%20Traffic%20was%20crazy%20that%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20sorry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2029-year-old%2C%20sheepish%20as%20we%20shook%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELim%20was%20easy%20to%20find%20online%2C%20and%20once%20I%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20her%2C%20she%20was%20keen%20to%20talk.%20She%20has%20some%20175%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%2C%20where%20she%20posts%20roughly%20twice%20or%20thrice%20a%20week%2C%20often%20glamour%20or%20fashion%20shots%20of%20herself.%20Lim%20told%20me%20her%20personal%20brand's%20focus%20is%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDJzIVU7SuwY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDJzIVU7SuwY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDJzIVU7SuwY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Abe%20Lim%20(%40abe.1)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20family%2C%20she%20said%2C%20runs%20a%20petrochemical%20business%20that%20she%20left%20to%20build%20a%20social%20media%20following%20as%20an%20environmentalist.%20In%202023%2C%20she%20ran%20for%20a%20local%20state%20parliament%20seat%20while%20campaigning%20on%20climate%20action%2C%20but%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELim's%20day%20job%20is%20running%20a%20plastics%20recycling%20company%20she%20founded%20in%202021.%20She%20posts%20photos%20from%20conferences%20and%20symposiums%20across%20Asia%20and%20the%20US%2C%20and%20snaps%20of%20herself%20on%20holiday%20in%20Bali%20and%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20array%20of%20photos%20found%20its%20way%20into%20the%20phones%20of%20men%20like%20Bilgi%C3%A7%20and%20Tozal%2C%20who%20believed%20%26quot%3BDora%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20charitable%20multimillionaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometime%20in%20late%202023%2C%20Lim%20said%2C%20she%20started%20receiving%20online%20messages%20from%20these%20men.%20She%20thought%20little%20of%20it%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20I've%20sort%20of%20put%20myself%20in%20the%20public%20spotlight%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20expected%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202024%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20men%20began%20contacting%20her%20friends%20and%20family%20and%20claiming%20she'd%20defrauded%20them%20out%20of%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20There%20were%20rumors%20of%20self-harm%20or%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20like%2C%20OK%2C%20this%20is%20serious%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e9ab080-3f46-4711-b354-612f212b7bbd%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20year%20went%20on%2C%20Lim%20was%20trapped%20in%20an%20escalating%20online%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMessages%20flooded%20her%20inbox%20and%20Instagram%20comments.%20She%20said%20she%20received%20dozens%20of%20emails%20and%20texts%20a%20day%20and%20showed%20me%20several%20on%20her%20phone.%20Lim%20was%20all%20smiles%20in%20her%20interview%2C%20but%20her%20fatigue%20and%20frustration%20were%20palpable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20mentally%20draining%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20heartbroken%20men%20tried%20to%20rekindle%20a%20nonexistent%20relationship%20with%20her%3B%20others%20sent%20threats%2C%20she%20said.%20For%20the%20first%20few%20months%20of%202024%2C%20she%20told%20me%2C%20she%20feared%20leaving%20her%20home%20in%20Malaysia.%20Lim%20now%20tries%20to%20delay%20her%20social%20media%20posts%20by%20a%20few%20days%20to%20keep%20her%20live%20location%20secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20messages%20that%20said%20like%3A%20'I'll%20fly%20down%20to%20kill%20you%2C%20track%20you%20down%20and%20make%20you%20pay%20for%20what%20you%20did%2C'%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20screenshots%20show%20messages%20from%20victims%20who%20blamed%20Lim%20for%20their%20losses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689d832c194a2d49b8ae8b9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20men%20sent%20Lim%20multiple%20messages%20accusing%20her%20of%20stealing%20their%20money%2C%20while%20others%2C%20like%20in%20the%20screenshot%20on%20the%20right%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20friends.%3Cp%3EAbe%20Lim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20were%20divided%20on%20whether%20Lim%20was%20%26quot%3BDora%26quot%3B%20or%20an%20unwitting%20victim%20of%20someone%20pretending%20to%20be%20her.%20Some%2C%20like%20Bilgi%C3%A7%2C%20said%20she%20clearly%20wasn't%20the%20woman%20they%20had%20chatted%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20sent%20me%20recordings%20of%20their%20video%20calls%2C%20which%20showed%20East%20or%20Southeast%20Asian%20women%20holding%20up%20a%20hand%20or%20using%20a%20camera%20angle%20to%20obscure%20their%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternet%20connection%20is%20not%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20woman%20in%20one%20video%20I%20viewed.%20She%20was%20clearly%20not%20Lim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbde8036-b3b7-4373-a6de-ad414c7fc5a0%5C%22%3E'Should%20I%20compensate%20them%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Lim%20and%20I%20sipped%20tea%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20she%20explained%20how%20she%20was%20grappling%20with%20a%20dilemma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20personal%20brand%20living%20on%20Instagram%2C%20how%20much%20time%20should%20she%20spend%20defending%20her%20reputation%20and%20speaking%20out%20against%20scams%3F%20Should%20she%20stop%20posting%3F%20Her%20brand%20was%20about%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20not%20going%20to%20war%20against%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20platform%2C%20it's%20not%20that%20hard%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20do%20I%20want%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20person%20that%20combats%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20she%20posted%20several%20warnings%20about%20scams%20on%20Instagram.%20Some%20of%20the%20men%20were%20insisting%20she%20was%20liable%20for%20their%20losses%20because%20her%20images%20were%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20say%20they%20know%20it's%20not%20you%2C%20but%20it's%20your%20photos%20anyway%2C%20so%20you%20should%20take%20some%20responsibility%20of%20compensating%20them%20with%20some%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELim%20said%20she%20considered%20paying%20some%20of%20them%20until%20her%20family%20talked%20her%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20guilt%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%2C%20would%20these%20allegations%20have%20appeared%20if%20I%20had%20brought%20this%20up%20in%20public%20earlier%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a905ec76-528d-4fe7-bbe0-e4a50d49900a%5C%22%3E'Who%20are%20you%20going%20to%20sue%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJames%2C%20the%20UNODC%20cybercrime%20coordinator%2C%20said%20Lim%20fits%20the%20profile%20of%20a%20content%20creator%20whose%20images%20are%20farmed%20by%20scam%20rings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20actually%20just%20a%20third%20party%20that%20has%20nothing%20at%20all%20to%20do%20with%20anything%20in%20the%20scam%2C%20and%20they%20sometimes%20have%20to%20even%20suffer%20the%20legal%20consequences%20afterward.%20Because%2C%20who%20are%20you%20going%20to%20sue%3F%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20swindlers%2C%20Lim's%20account%20was%20perfect.%20She%20was%20not%20well-known%20enough%20for%20a%20target%20to%20recognize%20her%2C%20and%20she%20frequently%20posted%20photos%20of%20herself%20in%20new%20outfits%20or%20at%20public%20events%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wealth%20of%20content%20to%20exploit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnline%20footage%20and%20voice%20data%20can%20also%20be%20fed%20to%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20algorithm%20to%20create%20a%20face%20filter%20for%20use%20in%20video%20calls%2C%20James%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Lim's%20case%2C%20several%20victims%20sent%20me%20screenshots%20of%20video%20calls%20with%20scam%20workers%2C%20which%20appeared%20to%20feature%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupenn-student-olga-loiek-youtube-china-social-media-stole-face-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-empowered%20deepfake%20face%20filters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20photos%20show%20the%20difference%20between%20Abe%20Lim's%20genuine%20photos%20and%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20video%20call%20that%20likely%20used%20an%20AI-empowered%20face%20filter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688084473d5881a51c1dd2e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20the%20left%20is%20a%20photo%20of%20Abe%20Lim%20used%20to%20scam%20an%20American%20man%20in%20California%20who%20spoke%20to%20me%2C%20and%20on%20the%20right%20is%20a%20screenshot%20of%20his%20video%20calls%20with%20a%20scam%20worker%20posing%20as%20Lim.%3Cp%3EAbe%20Lim%20and%20screenshot%20from%20victim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20analyzing%20the%20screenshots%2C%20James%20said%20some%20images%20were%20highly%20suspicious%2C%20with%20tell-tale%20features%20of%20AI%20filters%20such%20as%20discoloration%20on%20the%20edges%20of%20the%20face%20and%20crispness%20around%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20varying%20chin%20shapes%20and%20neck%20bumps%20in%20the%20webcam%20images%20also%20indicated%20the%20victims%20were%20likely%20called%20by%20at%20least%20two%20different%20women%20using%20deepfake%20filters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20it%20is%20very%20likely%20the%20images%20with%20white%20are%20deepfakes%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20screenshots%20show%20a%20woman%20speaking%20to%20a%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689adb94194a2d49b8ae623d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJames%20said%20it%20is%20highly%20likely%20a%20woman%20used%20a%20deepfake%20face%20filter%20of%20Lim%20in%20this%20video%20call%20with%20a%20victim.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20scam%20victim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7a8ef75-42ce-486c-8063-2c003ba9e668%5C%22%3EFraudsters%2C%20roaming%20free%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELim%20said%20what%20frustrates%20her%20most%20is%20that%20she's%20reported%20dozens%20of%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20accounts%20using%20her%20name%20and%20photos.%20Many%20were%20not%20taken%20down.%20A%20Facebook%20search%20of%20her%20name%20shows%20her%20photos%20on%20a%20dozen%20accounts%20purported%20to%20be%20of%20women%20living%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20New%20York.%20Some%20claim%20to%20run%20a%20plastics%20recycling%20company%20with%20the%20same%20name%20as%20Lim's%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20verified%20account%20with%20this%20face%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20herself.%20%26quot%3BYou%20shouldn't%20allow%20an%20account%20with%20the%20same%20photo%20to%20stay%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221594%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20shows%20several%20accounts%20of%20the%20same%20person%20with%20profile%20photos%20taken%20from%20Lim's%20social%20media.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6880859b3d5881a51c1dd2ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20search%20for%20Lim's%20name%20on%20Facebook%20in%20July%20yielded%20over%20a%20dozen%20results%20for%20accounts%20that%20use%20her%20name%20and%20profile%20picture.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20via%20Facebook%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Meta%2C%20which%20runs%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20WhatsApp%2C%20told%20me%20via%20email%20that%20it%20was%20committed%20to%20keeping%20its%20platforms%20safe%20and%20that%20it%20continues%20to%20%26quot%3Binvest%20in%20detection%20technology%20and%20work%20with%20law%20enforcement%20to%20prosecute%20scammers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImpersonation%20is%20against%20Meta's%20policies%20and%20we%20remove%20these%20accounts%20when%20they're%20found%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20wrote.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20dealt%20with%201%20billion%20fake%20accounts%20on%20its%20platforms%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20this%20year.%20Meta%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20Lim's%20case%20specifically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegally%2C%20Lim%20can't%20do%20much%20to%20compel%20Meta%2C%20which%20is%20headquartered%20in%20California%2C%20to%20take%20down%20accounts%20using%20her%20images%2C%20said%20Eric%20Goldman%2C%20the%20codirector%20of%20the%20High%20Tech%20Law%20Institute%20at%20Santa%20Clara%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Facebook%20may%20have%20no%20obligation%20to%20intervene%20to%20shut%20down%20or%20correct%20scam%20accounts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20US%20law%20protects%20social%20media%20firms%20from%20liability%20for%20third-party%20content%20posted%20on%20their%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bilgi%C3%A7%20and%20other%20victims%20in%20Turkey%20have%20engaged%20local%20lawyers%20in%20hopes%20of%20suing%20whoever%20took%20their%20money%20or%20compelling%20their%20arrest.%20It'll%20be%20a%20long%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20general%20principle%20of%20criminal%20law.%20If%20you%20cannot%20find%20the%20person%20committing%20the%20crime%2C%20your%20hands%20are%20tied%2C%26quot%3B%20Tar%C4%B1k%20G%C3%BClery%C3%BCz%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20Turkish%20law%20firm%20G%C3%BClery%C3%BCz%20Partners%2C%20told%20me%20about%20the%20country's%20legal%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%2C%20the%20UNODC%20anti-cybercrime%20coordinator%2C%20said%20perpetrators%20know%20the%20world's%20law%20enforcement%20system%20is%20ill-equipped%20to%20deal%20with%20pig-butchering%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dozens%20of%20phones%20and%20computer%20monitors%20are%20shown%20after%20being%20confiscated%20by%20authorities%20in%20Cambodia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689d8c5da17a8c5b4052da18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScam%20centers%2C%20such%20as%20this%20one%20raided%20in%20Cambodia%2C%20often%20run%20multiple%20pig-butchering%20schemes%20at%20a%20time%2C%20with%20a%20network%20of%20phones%20and%20computers%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20and%20dupe%20unsuspecting%20victims.%3Cp%3ETR%2FPOOL%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20victim's%20best%20hope%20is%20an%20international%20coalition%20involving%20Turkey%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20wherever%20the%20culprits%20are%20located%2C%20James%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20a%20country%20with%20considerable%20influence%20in%20Laos%20and%20Cambodia%2C%20has%20performed%20cross-border%20raids%20there%2C%20mostly%20against%20scam%20rings%20targeting%20Chinese%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20countries%20like%20Turkey%20and%20Malaysia%2C%20nearly%205%2C200%20miles%20apart%2C%20the%20best%20the%20men%20can%20do%20is%20hope%20and%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20Lim%20is%20posting%20frequently%20on%20social%20media%20and%20is%20trying%20to%20grow%20her%20brand%20as%20an%20environmentalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20lost%20was%20some%20reputation%20and%20photos.%20I%20didn't%20lose%20money%2C%20I%20didn't%20go%20through%20heartbreak%20with%20someone%20who%20didn't%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20she%20enrolled%20in%20a%20master's%20program%20for%20sustainable%20development%20management%20at%20Sunway%20University%20in%20Selangor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%2C%20who%20lost%20his%20life%20savings%20to%20%26quot%3BDora%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20also%20trying%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20wife%20was%20furious%20with%20him%2C%20and%20when%20I%20asked%20last%20month%20how%20their%20relationship%20was%20faring%2C%20Tozal%20said%20he's%20just%20trying%20to%20focus%20on%20working%20to%20support%20his%20family.%20He%20travels%20to%20see%20his%20children%20once%20every%20six%20months%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESitting%20in%20the%20kitchen%20of%20the%20Uzbek%20flat%20he%20shares%20with%20a%20roomm