h%20a%20relative%20sparked%20a%20newfound%20passion.%20This%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20career%20change%3B%20it%20marked%20a%20transformative%20shift%20in%20his%20perspective%20on%20farming%20and%20community%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeekeeping%2C%20as%20Jagpal%20discovered%2C%20offers%20several%20advantages%20over%20conventional%20farming%20practices.%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20eco-friendly%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBees%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20pollination%2C%20which%20is%20a%20vital%20component%20of%20agriculture.%20Introducing%20beehives%20into%20a%20farm%20boosts%20pollination%20rates%2C%20leading%20to%20higher%20yields%20for%20farmers%20in%20a%20radius%20of%20up%20to%20two%20kilometres.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FIMG_9316-1755149575.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Beekeeping%20requires%20a%20one-time%20investment%20and%20provides%20yields%20year%20after%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FIMG_9316-1755149575.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FIMG_9316-1755149575-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FIMG_9316-1755149575-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FIMG_9316-1755149575-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FIMG_9316-1755149575-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-486948%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBeekeeping%20requires%20a%20one-time%20investment%20and%20provides%20yields%20year%20after%20year.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20localised%20pollination%20benefit%20is%20particularly%20significant%20in%20water-scarce%20regions%20where%20optimising%20crop%20yields%20is%20paramount.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20the%20most%20important%20aspect%20is%20that%20beekeeping%20does%20not%20require%20any%20recurring%20expenses.%20With%20just%20one%20time%20investment%2C%20anyone%20can%20reap%20benefits%20year%20after%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20Jagpal%20began%20meeting%20bee%20farmers%20in%20Ludhiana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20beekeeping.%20He%20purchased%2030%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354377%2Fkerala-r-vishwan-honey-farmer-abandoned-child-bee-rearing-beekeeping-training-profits-inspiring%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebee%20boxes%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20a%20farmer%20in%20Delhi%2C%20investing%20Rs%2060%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20at%20Rs%202%2C000%20per%20box.%20Without%20any%20formal%20training%2C%20he%20relied%20on%20learning%20from%20other%20farmers%20and%20his%20own%20hands-on%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20encounter%20with%20bees%2C%20however%2C%20was%20far%20from%20pleasant.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20removing%20a%20hive%20frame%2C%20bees%20stung%20me%20in%20the%20eyes%2C%20leaving%20them%20badly%20swollen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20happened%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20bee%20behaviour%20at%20the%20time.%20But%20my%20passion%20kept%20me%20going.%20Instead%20of%20being%20scared%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20how%20bees%20behave.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20removing%20the%20frame%20from%20the%20box%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20do%20it%20gently%20to%20avoid%20shocking%20the%20bees.%20Also%2C%20avoid%20wearing%20perfumes%2C%20aromatic%20hair%20oils%2C%20or%20black%20clothing%2C%20as%20these%20can%20irritate%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20continuing%20his%20teaching%20job%2C%20Jagpal%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277897%2Fgujarat-couple-organic-chemical-free-farming-beekeping-svadya-raw-honey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epractising%20beekeeping%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20side.%20After%20mastering%20the%20nuances%20of%20the%20trade%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20quit%20teaching%20in%202007%20to%20devote%20himself%20fully%20to%20beekeeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20over%20500%20fellow%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagpal%20raises%20the%20Apis%20mellifera%20variety%20of%20honey%20bees.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20variety%20offers%20high%20production%20and%20boosts%20pollination.%20During%20the%20flowering%20season%2C%20honey%20can%20be%20harvested%20within%20just%2010%20days.%20On%20average%2C%20I%20get%20around%2040%20kg%20of%20honey%20per%20box%20annually%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-2-1733830180.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apart%20from%20honey%2C%20Jagpal%20sells%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20byproducts%20like%20beeswax%2C%20soap%2C%20bee%20pollen%2C%20and%20royal%20jelly.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-2-1733830180.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-2-1733830180-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-2-1733830180-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-2-1733830180-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2