s%20in%20each%20city%2C%20and%20we%20get%20them%20together%20for%20dinners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobinhood%20went%20public%20in%202021%20and%20is%20now%20worth%20about%20%2498.4%20billion.%20It%20had%202%2C300%20full-time%20employees%20as%20of%20December%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETenev%20said%20he%20didn't%20want%20the%20group%20to%20become%20150%20people%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20top%20of%20the%20org%20chart%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20includes%20people%20who%20have%20the%20most%20impact%20at%20every%20level%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20added%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bvery%20much%26quot%3B%20concentrates%20promotions%20within%20top%20performers%20and%20rewards%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20people%20in%20the%20company%26quot%3B%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobinhood%20declined%20further%20comment%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETenev%20isn't%20the%20first%20to%20launch%20a%20secretive%2C%20invite-only%20company%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Fortune%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-q3-earnings-aapl-stock-price-iphone-demand-ai-tariffs-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20an%20exclusive%20club%20for%20top%20performers%20called%20the%20Top%20100.%20It%20was%20described%20as%20an%20invitation-only%2C%20off-site%20meeting%20held%20for%20the%20100%20most%20influential%20people%20at%20Apple%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20official%20position%20or%20tenure.%20Employees%20participated%20in%20a%20three-day%20strategy%20session%20focused%20on%20top-secret%20projects%20and%20how%20upcoming%20products%20will%20be%20unveiled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20comment%20asking%20if%20these%20off-sites%20or%20similar%20events%20for%20top%20employees%20still%20take%20place%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobinhood-ceo-club-of-150-best-employ