Kelly%20Benthall%2C%2054%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20retired%20early%20and%20have%20now%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-early-genx-couple-travel-fear-setting-unfamiliar-places-nightmare-2025-5%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eslow%20traveling%20for%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20summer%2C%20they%20spent%20five%20fast-paced%20weeks%20moving%20through%20seven%20stops%20across%20the%20UK%20and%20Ireland.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20experience%20left%20her%20exhausted%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reminded%20the%20couple%20why%20they'd%20chosen%20a%20slower%2C%20more%20intentional%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPlain%20and%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20hold%20the%20tomatoes%20%E2%80%94%20fast%20travel%20is%20exhausting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20Nigel%20and%20I%20retired%20early%20last%20year%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-early-genx-couple-slow-travel-career-skills-champagne-test-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eslow%20travel%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We've%20made%20it%20a%20habit%20to%20stay%20in%20one%20place%20for%20a%20month.%20It%20feels%20long%20enough%20to%20unpack%2C%20exhale%2C%20and%20feel%20like%20we%20live%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20summer%2C%20we%20broke%20our%20own%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20planned%20a%20five-week%20sprint%20through%20the%20UK%20and%20Ireland%20%E2%80%94%20seven%20stops%20in%20quick%20succession%2C%20most%20just%20five%20days%20long.%20We%20started%20in%20Dorset%20with%20a%20brief%2C%20emotionally%20heavy%20family%20visit%2C%20then%20made%20our%20way%20through%20Cornwall%2C%20the%20Cotswolds%2C%20the%20Lake%20District%2C%20Edinburgh%2C%20North%20Wales%2C%20and%20finally%20ended%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-going-to-dublin-first-time-from-american-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethree-day%20finale%20in%20Dublin%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20part%20memory%20lane%2C%20part%20reunion%20tour%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20intentional%20sightseeing.%20Some%20stops%20held%20memories%20for%20Nigel%2C%20others%20were%20entirely%20new.%20It%20was%20a%20chance%20for%20both%20of%20us%20to%20explore%20his%20home%20country%20with%20fresh%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20packed%20in%20everything%20from%20castles%20and%20sea%20cliffs%20to%20wild%20ponies%2C%20old%20friends%2C%20long%20walks%2C%20and%20short%20pub%20chats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20like%20an%20affair%2C%20not%20with%20a%20person%2C%20but%20with%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20travel.%20A%20thrilling%2C%20nostalgic%2C%20completely%20unsustainable%20fling%20with%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELove%20Business%20Insider%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fpreferences%2Fsource%3Fq%3Dbusinessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdd%20Business%20Insider%20as%20a%20preferred%20source%20on%20Google%20to%20see%20more%20of%20us.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kelly%20Benthall%20and%20her%20husband%20with%20hoods%20and%20clouds%20in%20the%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689ca4a3cfc04e97619b550b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKelly%20Benthall%20and%20her%20husband's%20five-week%2C%20seven-stop%20trip%20across%20the%20UK%20and%20Ireland%20confirmed%20they%20prever%20slow%20travel.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Kelly%20Benthall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20numbers%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E5%20weeks%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E7%20stops%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E4%20home-cooked%20reunions%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2%2C000%2B%20miles%20driven%20in%20a%20tiny%20car%20on%20even%20tinier%20roads%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E178%20mapped%20stops%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECountless%20pints%20and%20pies%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20whirlwind%20of%20firsts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2267d9df6a-a793-4170-9ef7-ea56b4a0fd3b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22It%20was%20a%20whirlwind%20of%20firsts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20the%20crash%5C%22%3EBurning%20through%20cash%20and%20energy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20my%20legs%20were%20stronger%20than%20ever%2C%20thanks%20to%20all%20the%20walking%20and%20staircases%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20which%20felt%20too%20narrow%20for%20a%20modern%20human%20with%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20rest%20of%20me%20shut%20down.%20After%20Dublin%2C%20when%20we%20finally%20arrived%20at%20our%20more%20long-term%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Flong-term-airbnbs-monthly-rentals-sublet-faq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emonthlong%20Airbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Killaloe%2C%20Ireland%2C%20I%20slept%20for%20a%20full%20day.%20Even%20after%20that%2C%20I%20felt%20drained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20days%20in%2C%20my%20mind%20was%20still%20on%20high%20alert%20%E2%80%94%20scanning%20for%20surprises%2C%20wrong%20turns%2C%20or%20a%20crowd%20around%20the%20corner.%20That%20internal%20alarm%20system%20%E2%80%94%20so%20helpful%20while%20navigating%20new%20terrain%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20switch%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-travel-for-rich-americans-luxury-vacation-budgets-spending-slowdown-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espent%20more%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20usual.%20Without%20monthlong%20Airbnb%20discounts%20or%20home-cooked%20meals%2C%20the%20costs%20added%20up.%20We%20indulged%20in%20well-regarded%20restaurants%20nearly%20every%20day%2C%20and%20we%20felt%20it%20in%20both%20our%20budget%20and%20our%20waistlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20late%20nights%20too%20%E2%80%94%202%20a.m.%20pub%20closings%20and%20dance%20floors%20I%20used%20to%20k