t%20competing%20for%20farmland.%20We%20just%20need%20stronger%20policy%20support%2C%20pilot%20projects%20on%20government-owned%20reservoirs%2C%20and%20technology%20adapted%20for%20local%20needs.%20India%20can%20also%20look%20abroad%20for%20lessons.%20Countries%20like%20China%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20even%20island%20nations%20like%20the%20Maldives%20have%20embraced%20FPV%20thanks%20to%20geography%20and%20policy%20support.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20turning%20that%20potential%20into%20reality%20will%20mean%20addressing%20some%20tough%20hurdles%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20challenges%20under%20the%20surface%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20to%20FPV%20adoption%20isn%E2%80%99t%20entirely%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigher%20upfront%20costs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20FPV%20costs%20seven%20to%2010%20percent%20more%20than%20ground-mounted%20solar%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20floating%20platforms%2C%20which%20make%20up%20about%2035%20percent%20of%20project%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EData%20gaps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Many%20water%20bodies%20remain%20unmapped%20for%20solar%20potential%2C%20hampering%20design%20and%20impact%20assessment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20impacts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Some%20mega-projects%20have%20disrupted%20fishing%20livelihoods.%20For%20generations%2C%20fishermen%20depended%20on%20these%20waters%2C%20but%20are%20now%20barred%20from%20accessing%20them.%20They%20say%20officials%20surveyed%20affected%20families%20yet%20offered%20no%20support%2C%20and%20that%20promised%20jobs%20in%20the%20project%20have%20not%20materialised%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20basic%20labour%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20tailored%20standards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Current%20solar%20module%20standards%20are%20for%20land-based%20systems%3B%20floating%20arrays%20face%20unique%20challenges%20like%20humidity%20and%20corrosion.%3