gh%20the%20global%20FidoNet%20network.%20This%20led%20to%20my%20participation%20in%20INET%20conferences%2C%20where%20I%20advocated%20for%20public%20internet%20access%20in%20India.%20Given%20the%20security%20policies%20then%2C%20only%20government-linked%20bodies%20could%20launch%20the%20internet.%20VSNL%20was%20ideal%2C%20as%20it%20had%20existing%20lease%20lines%20and%20global%20partnerships.%20This%20led%20to%20meetings%20with%20VSNL%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20internet%20revolution%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Suchit%20Nanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanda%E2%80%99s%20pioneering%20spirit%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20advocacy.%20His%20tech%20firm%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20receive%20an%20internet%20licence%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20(DoT).%20He%20played%20a%20trailblazing%20role%20in%20expanding%20digital%20access%20through%20the%20development%20of%20internet%20set-top%20boxes%20(STBs)%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20the%20web%20to%20television%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20innovative%20ventures%20like%20Nanda%20Netcom%20and%20Jadoonet.com%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20tech%20giants%20Samsung%20and%20Intel%2C%20he%20helped%20make%20the%20internet%20more%20accessible%20to%20Indian%20households%2C%20redefining%20how%20people%20connected%20and%20consumed%20digital%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20launch%3A%20VSNL%E2%80%99s%20gateway%20to%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Independence%20Day%20in%201995%2C%20the%20GIAS%20public%20internet%20service%20by%20VSNL%20was%20launched%20and%20opened%20to%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-500x533.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22internet%20launch%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-500x533.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-281x300.jpg%20281w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-768x818.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-150x160.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300.jpg%201080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485562%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20dial-up%20capacity%20was%20limited%20to%20just%2016%20or%2032%20lines%2C%20and%20we%20had%20access%20to%20only%20four%20Class%20C%20IP%20addresses%20from%20APNIC%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Neeraj%20Sonker%2C%20who%20served%20as%20General%20Manager%2C%20Internet%20Services%20at%20VSNL%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20the%20internet%20in%20India%20was%20only%20available%20to%20educational%20and%20research%20institutes%20via%20ERNET%20(the%20first%20internet%20connection%20to%20India)%2C%20NICNET%20(for%20government%20only)%2C%20and%20STP%20(for%20tech%20parks%20only).%20The%20public%20internet%20service%20was%20a%20milestone.%20The%20GIAS%20launch%20was%20just%20the%20start%20%E2%80%94%20it%20opened%20the%20floodgates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%3A%20pioneers%20and%20partnerships%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20helped%20shape%20the%20backend%20systems%20and%20rollout%20strategy%2C%20using%20our%20experience%20running%20a%20nationwide%20BBS%20network.%20A%20close%20group%20of