ssing%20customer%20and%20media%20criticism%20in%20the%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20highlights%20how%2C%20despite%20limited%20network%20expertise%20and%20resources%2C%20the%20team%20managed%20to%20connect%20major%20cities%20through%20a%2064-kbps%20satellite%20link%2C%20established%20Points%20of%20Presence%20(POPs)%20across%20India%2C%20provided%20dial-up%20and%20leased%20line%20services%2C%20and%20later%20expanded%20the%20network%20to%20Tier%202%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20leadership%20also%20saw%20the%20rollout%20of%20key%20innovations%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20shift%20from%20static%20to%20dynamic%20network%20routing%20and%20improvements%20in%20customer%20support%20and%20billing%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20users%3A%20The%20internet%20guide%20and%20community%20building%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20team%20continued%20to%20upgrade%20infrastructure%20and%20expand%20services%2C%20attention%20increasingly%20turned%20to%20empowering%20customers%20to%20navigate%20the%20new%20digital%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20pivotal%20initiative%20in%20this%20direction%20was%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Internet%20User%20Guide%20(The%20Guide)%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20both%20customers%20and%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20need%20for%20user%20empowerment%2C%20the%20team%2C%20at%20Nanda%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%2C%20enlisted%20Stanford%20Professor%20Dr%20Raj%20Mehta%20to%20craft%20the%20Internet%20User%20Guide.%20Dr%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20hands-on%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20fielding%20late-night%20calls%20and%20emails%20from%20users%20nationwide%20%E2%80%94%20reflected%20the%20spirit%20of%20collaboration%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20digital%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Mehta%20returned%20to%20India%20during%20that%20time%20and%20dedicated%20significant%20effort%20to%20assisting%20VSNL%20and%20end-users.%20In%201997%2C%20the%20spiral-bound%2